=Be Yourself=

9
00:00:53,888 --> 00:00:56,672
=Episode 9=

10
00:00:57,359 --> 00:00:59,039
This sudden thunder.

11
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:00,920
What happened, exactly?

12
00:01:01,079 --> 00:01:02,639
Is Feiyang in some trouble?

13
00:01:04,639 --> 00:01:05,319
Young Master.

14
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:07,039
I'm really sorry.

15
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:08,560
We didn't host you well this time.

16
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:10,840
No problem.

17
00:01:11,119 --> 00:01:11,720
Next time.

18
